verses.verse: The YY <S%H3068><s%> reigneth <S%H4427><s%> <S%H8804><s%>, he is clothed <S%H3847><s%> <S%H8804><s%> with majesty <S%H1348><s%>; the YY <S%H3068><s%> is clothed <S%H3847><s%> <S%H8804><s%> with strength <S%H5797><s%>, wherewith he hath girded <S%H247><s%> <S%H8694><s%> himself: the world <S%H8398><s%> also is stablished <S%H3559><s%> <S%H8735><s%>, that it cannot be moved <S%H4131><s%> <S%H8735><s%>.
